/PhaseField/cmake-build-release/

# Build directories
**/build/
**/cmake-build-*/

# IDE
**/.idea/
**/.DS_Store

# Results (regenerated by running tests)
**/*_results/
**/mms_results/
**/ch_results/
**/Results/

# MMS convergence-rate outputs (regenerated by tests)
**/mms/Rates/*.csv

# Stray logs and one-off diagnostic images
*.log
**/*.log
**/diagnostics_comparison.png

# Python cache from analysis scripts
**/__pycache__/

# Backup binaries (manual snapshots, not version-controlled)
**/ferrofluid.backup_*

# Archives and large files
*.zip

# Reference material (papers, etc.)
**/Reference/
**/References/*.pdf

# Claude worktrees
**/.claude/
